{"data":[{"id":562615571,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"e4fae1c8e6fecff65ead0c428bfc222d","url_token":"zhuang-ya-de","name":"装丫的","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/e4fae1c8e6fecff65ead0c428bfc222d","user_type":"people","headline":"工程师","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":6,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562615571","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546113557,"updated_time":1546113557,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":37,"comment_count":8,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e如果我是清华数学系主任，看到你这个问题我会发布一条微博说：“无论那个高中生证明哥德巴赫猜想，都不会被清华北大数学系保送”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e难道解决一个世界级难题都不配保送清华大学么？当然配，真做到了你都有资格当系主任了。但是如果真的证明哥德巴赫猜想可以保送清华大学，这样子会有多少“学渣”高中生为此耽误终身。对此，请参考其他答主的回答，希望你能体会到我想说的是什么了吧。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e现在说说我自己的故事吧：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e答主本科数学系，寒假回老家。老家的亲戚都夸我9岁的表弟是个数学天才，数学特别厉害连计算机都不如他快。于是乎莫名其妙的就拉着9表弟和我这个海龟留学生比试比试，我也被迫应战了。结果那货上来就抛出什么类似于：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=2253-127%3D%EF%BC%9F%EF%BC%9B46%2A25%3D%EF%BC%9F+%EF%BC%9B8%2A543%3D%EF%BC%9F\" alt=\"2253-127=？；46*25=？ ；8*543=？\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这样的问题，结果我当我说出想要个草稿纸的时候就招到了一众的鄙视。9岁的表弟分秒内就用不知道从哪学来的速算法一一答出，确实对于这种简单的加减乘除口算比计算器快多了。之后不明所以的七大姑八大姨更是一顿嘲讽，说我在外面这几年是不是压根没读书啊，你每次都说读书很累怎么数学系出来的连一个小学生比不过啊。还说什么干脆让9岁的表弟和我换一换他去美国读大学，我回笼重新上小学。最后搞得我是一脸尴尬，家里人无地自容。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e确实，不管是对我9岁的表弟，还是那些终日在地里干活的亲戚来说这些加减乘除已经是他们能想到的最难数学题了，甚至是数学的全部。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e其实他们不知道，我也没办法短时间让他们知道数学的全貌远不只这些。同理，哥德巴赫猜想猜想看似是小学生都能理解的一句话：任一大于2的偶数都可写成两个质数之和。其实证明方法已经触及到最前沿的数论论文，而仅仅只是理解现有论文，哪怕是对于一个数学系博士生都是一个不小的挑战，如果论文和研究方向不一致的话那和看天书也没啥区别了。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"如果我是清华数学系主任，看到你这个问题我会发布一条微博说：“无论那个高中生证明哥德巴赫猜想，都不会被清华北大数学系保送” 难道解决一个世界级难题都不配保送清华大学么？当然配，真做到了你都有资格当系主任了。但是如果真的证明哥德巴赫猜想可以保…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=70\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotatio